This library is a modernized redesign of the application-server layer from the
"BackBone" framework suite originally authored by Tetsunori Matsubara at
Sun Microsystems (circa 2000–2005). It is built on the shazo persistence
abstraction (https://github.com/juanitadevelopment/shazo).
